@prgeor: 
I confirmed the bugs this PR addresses are fixed. Tested with build id [207726](https://sonic-build.azurewebsites.net/ui/sonic/pipelines/138/builds/207726/artifacts?branchName=master).

Somewhere it says 'review required' ... what else has to be done to review this PR?

@lguohan this change lgtm.
I don't recall why we initially hardcoded the flash_size as an attribute for each product instead of just relying on automatic detection.
On some products we do use this mechanism to ensure consistent behavior across all the switches which might have shipped with different flash sizes.

@dgsudharsan did you test the following cases

1. Device already running with latest CPLD and then firmware upgrade skips CPLD upgrade
2. Device has old CPLD and firmware upgrade upgrades to higher version?

